<style type="text/css">
    .modifier-row {display:flex; width:100%; align-items: center; margin-bottom:5px;}
</style>
<div class="text-field">
    <p>{{name}} is requesting a Recall Knowledge check using their Esoteric Lore skill{{#if targ.name}} against the {{targ.name}}{{/if}}.</p>
    <p>Action/Feat References: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.1OagaWtBpVXExToo]{Recall Knowledge} @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.cvQmPkJtybMcHinK]{Esoteric Lore} @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.1Bt7uCW2WI4sM84P]{Dubious Knowledge} {{#if hasDiverseLore}}@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.KlqKpeq5OmTRxVHb]{Diverse Lore}{{/if}}</p>
    <p>DC References: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.journals.JournalEntry.S55aqwWIzpQRFhcq.JournalEntryPage.dRu66xNqJ9Ihe1or]{Difficulty Classes}</p>
    <fieldset style=`border: 1px; border-radius: 25px;`>
        <legend>Roll Settings</legend>
        <span class="modifier-row">
            <label for="el-modifier">Esoteric Lore DC Modifier: </label>
            <input type="number" id="el-modifier" value="{{esotericLoreModifier}}"/>
        </span>
        <span class="modifier-row">
            <label for="target">Target: </label>
            <select name="target" id="target">
                <option value="0">Haunt, Curse, or Creature</option>
                {{#if hasDiverseLore}}
                <option value="-2">Anything (-2)</option>
                {{/if}}
            </select>
        </span>
        <hr>
        <span class="modifier-row">
            <label for="dc">Raw DC (excluding any modifiers above): </label>
            <input type="number" id="dc" value="{{targ.dc}}"/>
        </span>
    </fieldset>
</div>